---
title: Creamy Alfredo-Style Shrimp Linguine with Bacon and Peas
description: All the elements in this dish are classics that are made for one another. Shrimp, bacon and spinach have nothing but love for one another and couldn't pair better with a creamy sauce and pasta. Enjoy!
